Quest._questDescription: Demetrius needs a fresh melon for his research.
Quest.targetMessage: This is perfect! It's just what I need for my research. It's going to be hard not to eat it! Thanks a bunch.

Quest._questDescription: George needs a hot pepper to soothe his aching knee.
Quest.targetMessage: Took you long enough... hmmph... Well it's good and spicy at least. Thanks.

Quest._currentObjective: Bring Marnie one bunch of amaranth.
Quest._questDescription: Marnie wants to give her cows a special treat. She's asking for a single bunch of amaranth.
Quest.targetMessage: Oh, the amaranth I asked for! Thank you so much... my cows are going to love this!$h

Quest._questDescription: Willy is challenging you to catch a squid. He says you can fish them from the ocean on winter nights.
Quest.targetMessage: Hey, you did it! Not bad. Not bad at all. I'm impressed.#$b#Winter's a good time to break out the old fishing rod, isn't it?

Quest._questDescription: Gus wants to make fish stew, but he needs an albacore.
Quest.targetMessage: *sniff*...*sniff*... What's that? Something smells like albacore!#$b#Aha! You brought it! Thanks a million!

Quest._questDescription: Emily wants a taste of spring. She's asking for a fresh apricot.
Quest.targetMessage: Oh... You followed through! Thanks, this looks delicious!$h

Quest._questDescription: Pierre will pay "top coin" to whoever brings him a plate of sashimi. Apparently he's really craving the stuff.
Quest.targetMessage: It's about time! I was starting to get the shakes, I wanted this fish so bad. *munch*... Mmm, now that's good.#$b#Thanks, @.$h

Quest._questDescription: Demetrius is studying the toxin levels of the local pufferfish. He'd like you to bring him one.
Quest.targetMessage: There you are. The specimen looks perfect. I'm going to get it on ice straight away. Thanks, @!

Quest._questDescription: Kent wants to give his wife a starfruit for their anniversary.
Quest.targetMessage: Hey. Shhh... Don't let Jodi see.#$b#Ah, this looks juicy. She'll love it. Thank you so much.$h

Quest._questDescription: Gus put out a notice requesting a fresh lobster.
Quest.targetMessage: Something smells like fresh lobster. Oh, that's good.$h#$b#Take care, friend.

Quest._questDescription: Pam's TV Remote is dead. She's having a tough time going back and forth between the couch and the TV dial.
Quest.targetMessage: Hey, you pulled through with the battery pack! Thanks, kid... You're a life-saver!$h

Quest._questDescription: Willy is challenging you to catch a Lingcod.
Quest.targetMessage: Hey, that's a real lunker! You've certainly got the angler's blood in you.$h

Item.name: Paint Bucket
Item.Name: Paint Bucket
Item.description: Allows you to apply different textures to supported objects.
